text: Maria thought speaking out of the question, then, you expect to go to, cook?

passages.fragment: Maria thought speaking out of the question ,
passages.full_quote: <used>Maria thought speaking out of the question, a</used>nd the gentlemen did nothing but eat and admire

passages.fragment: out of the question , then , you
passages.full_quote: Leaving superiority <used>out of the question, then, you</used> must still agree to receive my orders now and then, without being piqued or hurt by the tone of command
"So, <used>then, you expect to go</used> up into our main-top, do you, cook, when you are dead"

passages.full_quote: "Where do <used>you expect to go to, cook</used>?"
